title: Mo Amer
itunes:title: Mo Amer
description:
Stand-up comedian Mo Amer tells Whitney about fleeing war, asking his 4th grade teacher for a rubber, and why he hasn’t watched porn in years.  Mo’s critically acclaimed show MO is streaming now on Netflix along with his comedy specials THE VAGABOND and MOHAMMED IN TEXAS.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
